    {
      "id": "1523722665972732135",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-07-06T16:09:52.966+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "```\n  co_5a_ncomp_butted = ncomp.interacting(pcomp).not_overlapping(pcomp)\n  co_ncomp_check = contact.interacting(co_5a_ncomp_butted)\n\n  co5a_l1 = co_ncomp_check.enclosed(co_5a_ncomp_butted, 0.1.um, euclidian)\n  co5a_l1.output('CO.5a', 'CO.5a : Nplus overlap of contact on COMP (butted N+/P+) : 0.1µm')\n```",
      "author": {
        "id": "596068704471482370",
        "name": "246tnt",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "tnt",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "2026-07_media/88d17af9d19ab43565b0c46751ef7d12-DFEE5.png"
      },
      "attachments": [],
      "embeds": [],
      "stickers": [],
      "reactions": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "inlineEmojis": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1523722754581598331",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-07-06T16:10:14.092+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "And instead I'd recommend :\n\n```\n  co5a_l1 = co_ncomp_check.enclosed(nplus, 0.1.um, euclidian)\n```",
